Behavioral Summary

Serial: Users now see a banner, help, command list, and prompt; simpler syntax with clear feedback. // Improves discoverability and reduces input friction without altering signal behavior.
UI: On-screen preset selection instantly applies a pattern; custom entry allows parameterized builds with an Apply button to commit. // Mirrors CLI command set through a touchscreen-like interface pattern; ready to back a real display driver